Name
       timing_socv_sigma_spatial_multiplier

Syntax
       timing_socv_sigma_spatial_multiplier

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       Provides a fractional percentage multiplier, which allows you to select
       some (or all, none) of  the spatial derate to be applied.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

